Entries.default: "Aimico, it is good to see you! It has been several years, no?"
Entries.female: "Aimica, it is good to see you! It has been several years, no?"

Entries.default: "Agracima for protecting me from the Doemenels."
"The Vailian Trading Company was not so forgiving. But I am glad to be alive."
"The Rauataians, they are stern. But I think they finally recognize my talents! Ac, I am moving up with them."
"They promoted me to overseer of Sanitary Engineering. Last month I was only the assistant. Quite a step, no?"
"Ac, it is a very important job. In fact, I should probably return to it."
